{"tid":947860,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個擊退煩膠健身美容sales既經歷","createTime":"2018-12-19T14:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T02:31:22.000Z","uid":220922,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e3210844b65f7336a54bccec185b90a812539a21","tid":947860,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：美容sales<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地呢個優惠做埋今日就冇架啦，你今日join啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想考慮下先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考慮完就冇架啦，聽日返黎我都係收你正價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁姐係冇得返去諗，要即刻買？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀 咁就最抵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁當我地冇緣，反正呢種package 周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健身sales<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有高低膊，不如join package 我地會幫你解決問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁貴，成800蚊一個鐘喎，我覺得唔值囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 身體健康好重要架，投資少少，將來回報都係你自己，有靚身材喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估你脊醫，我要比咁貴就比醫生啦，唔通比PT咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野好重要，就係一定要有自信<br />\n通常佢地好鍾意問你想改善咩地方<br />\n然後針住你個d地方攻擊<br />\n例如你想改善黑眼圈，佢地一定話你個樣好攰好殘，冇左黑眼圈一定係大美人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後你就會信，覺得自己好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以一定要覺得自己完美先冇缺點<br />\n話你肥殘醜，都一定要話我唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我對自己好滿意<br />\n唔好比佢地有機可乘"},{"pid":"bfd645bfe9fced337875ab36544844d274cf331d","tid":947860,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人有經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6315da3acb8af50cd66ca7b3bc5c3737d87e9da5","tid":947860,"uid":182399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddba3fa34c5dfa7b5c2d1b3e7919b3caa9a54d0","tid":947860,"uid":52824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"話我D筋唔夠鬆,上番幾堂拉筋,每堂幾百,我話我自己拉得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e97dfc2bbbf525d5a580141540174e5ddf52a1e","tid":947860,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}